entry.name: bind9_11_ssh
entry.description: Statistics from BIND DNS service version 9.11. Requires root (or sudo without prompt) level permissions in credentials stored as ssh.user/ssh.pass.
entry.technology: Requires working BIND DNS server. Build with 9.11. Modify snmpd.conf to execute the scripts that generate data. Copy the scripts to /etc/snmp/scripts/. Detailed information at https://github.com/sweenig/bind9-snmp.
